

Keywords:
		Search keywords: 	SV VMM vmm_rtl_config  

Technical content:
 
		Title: 		 VMM_RTL_CONFIG
 
		Objective:    Demonstrates the usage of RTL Configuration.

		Description:   This test shows the generation and usage of RTL configuartion. A two-pass process is used :
		               1. first pass to generate the RTL configuration to use.(+vmm_gen_rtl_config)
																	2. second pass to verify this configuartion.
																	
		Additional setup: None	
 
 To run the example:
      Using Makefile:
       	make clean           -- To clean up the log files and executable of previous run
       	make comp            -- To compile the design
        make run             -- To run the design
        make all             -- It does all the above steps.
 
 
Location Information:
		PATH: 			$VMM_HOME/examples/testbench/sv/vmm/std_lib/vmm_rtl_config
		DIAGRAMS: 		None
		Cross Reference:	$VMM_HOME/doc/vmm_user_guide.pdf
